sequenceDiagram
    participant "Operator (SRE/DevOps)" as OperatorSREDevOps
    participant "Monitoring Dashboard" as MonitoringDashboard
    participant "GitHub Actions CI/CD" as GitHubActionsCICD
    participant "Azure Kubernetes Service (AKS)" as AzureKubernetesServiceAKS
    participant "Azure Container Registry (ACR)" as AzureContainerRegistryACR

    activate OperatorSREDevOps
    MonitoringDashboard->>OperatorSREDevOps: 1. 1. [Alert] Critical SLO Breach Detected
    OperatorSREDevOps->>MonitoringDashboard: 2. 2. [Investigate] Analyze dashboard to confirm deployment failure
    MonitoringDashboard-->>OperatorSREDevOps: Correlate high error rate with recent deployment annotation
    OperatorSREDevOps->>OperatorSREDevOps: 3. 3. [Decision] Consult runbook and decide to execute rollback
    activate GitHubActionsCICD
    OperatorSREDevOps->>GitHubActionsCICD: 4. 4. [Identify & Trigger] Initiate 'Deploy' workflow with previous stable image tag
    GitHubActionsCICD-->>OperatorSREDevOps: Workflow run started successfully (HTTP 204)
    activate AzureKubernetesServiceAKS
    GitHubActionsCICD->>AzureKubernetesServiceAKS: 5. 5. [Execute Deployment] Apply new deployment state
    AzureKubernetesServiceAKS-->>GitHubActionsCICD: Deployment update acknowledged
    activate AzureContainerRegistryACR
    AzureKubernetesServiceAKS->>AzureContainerRegistryACR: 6. 6. [Pull Image] Request stable image 'v1.2.3'
    AzureContainerRegistryACR-->>AzureKubernetesServiceAKS: Image layers data
    AzureKubernetesServiceAKS->>AzureKubernetesServiceAKS: 7. 7. [Internal] Perform rolling update of pods
    OperatorSREDevOps->>MonitoringDashboard: 8. 8. [Validate] Monitor system health and deployment status
    MonitoringDashboard-->>OperatorSREDevOps: Observe metrics returning to baseline (error rate drops)
    OperatorSREDevOps->>OperatorSREDevOps: 9. 9. [Confirm & Communicate] Declare incident resolved

    note over AzureContainerRegistryACR: Assumption: Immutable container image tags (e.g., SemVer, Git SHA) are used. Mutable tags like 'l...

    deactivate AzureContainerRegistryACR
    deactivate AzureKubernetesServiceAKS
    deactivate GitHubActionsCICD
    deactivate OperatorSREDevOps
